<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Goth" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Goth,</orth> one of an ancient German tribe in the East of Europe: <cit><quote>Ovid was among the --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 3, 9</bibl></cit>. Often in Tit. (<bibl n="shak. ayl 1.28.9" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 28</bibl>. 85 etc.).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>